result:
div.padding-large
  div.flex.wide.justify-space-between
    //- :Left
    div: h2 Bookings

    //- Right
    div
      a.padding(@click="active='all'" :class="{'active':active=='all'}") All
      a.padding(@click="active='paid'" :class="{'active':active=='paid'}") Paid
      a.padding(@click="active='due'" :class="{'active':active=='due'}") Due
  
  //- Contents
  table.wide
    tr(v-for="booking in filteredBookings")
      td
        h3 {{booking.account_name}}
        h5 {{booking.booking_status}}
      td
        button.float-right(@click='$refs.booking.show(booking)') View

  modal(ref="booking" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.high-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding Booking Details
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            table.wide
              tr
                td Booked on
                td Fake 10, 2018
              tr
                td Schedule
                td Fake 10, 2018, Fake:00 am
              tr
                td Status
                td Fake Status
            div.flex.wide
              button.flex-grow Cancel Booking
              button.flex-grow.margin-left-small(@click="$store.dispatch('approveBooking',params.booking_id)") Approve Booking
              button.flex-grow.margin-left-small Reschedule
            form
                fieldset
                  details
                    summary Package Details
                    br
                    table.wide
                      tr
                        td Package Name
                        td Fake Package 1
                      tr
                        td Package Description
                        td Fake Description
                      tr
                        td Duration
                        td 30 fakes
                      tr
                        td Addons
                        td
                      tr
                        td Themes
                        td
                      tr
                        td Total Price
                        td Php 00.00
